('Plant', '智多星', 'Plant', '富有想象力和创造力，善于解决复杂问题，提供创新想法', 'Creative, imaginative, free-thinking. Generates ideas and solves difficult problems.', '聪明、好奇、独立思考、非传统', 'Creative, imaginative, unorthodox', '提供创新解决方案，解决复杂技术问题', 'Generates ideas, solves difficult problems', '忽视细节、不善于沟通、过于专注自己的想法', 'Might ignore incidentals, too preoccupied to communicate effectively'),
('Resource_Investigator', '资源调查者', 'Resource Investigator', '善于发现和探索机会，外向且充满好奇心', 'Outgoing, enthusiastic. Explores opportunities and develops contacts.', '外向、热情、好奇、沟通能力强', 'Extrovert, enthusiastic, communicative', '拓展人脉、获取资源、探索新机会', 'Explores opportunities, develops contacts', '容易失去兴趣、缺乏深度跟进', 'Might be over-optimistic, can lose interest once the initial enthusiasm has passed'),
('Coordinator', '协调者', 'Coordinator', '成熟的领导者，能引导团队向目标前进', 'Mature, confident, identifies talent. Clarifies goals. Delegates effectively.', '自信、有威望、善于识别他人优势', 'Mature, confident, good chairperson', '明确目标、分配任务、促进团队合作', 'Clarifies goals, promotes decision-making, delegates well', '可能操控他人、缺乏激情', 'Can be seen as manipulative, might offload their own share of the work'),
('Shaper', '推进者', 'Shaper', '充满活力和挑战精神，推动团队克服困难', 'Challenging, dynamic, thrives on pressure. Has the drive and courage to overcome obstacles.', '有干劲、竞争性强、意志坚定', 'Challenging, dynamic, thrives on pressure', '激发动力、推动进展、挑战低效', 'Shapes the way team effort is applied, directs attention generally to the setting of objectives and priorities', '易冲动、可能伤害他人感受', 'Can be seen as aggressive, might offend people''s feelings'),
('Monitor_Evaluator', '监督者', 'Monitor Evaluator', '冷静分析和判断，权衡利弊做出正确决策', 'Sober, strategic and discerning. Sees all options and judges accurately.', '冷静、有判断力、谨慎、逻辑性强', 'Sober, strategic, discerning', '评估方案、识别风险、做出明智决策', 'Judges accurately, weighs up the team''s options in a dispassionate way', '缺乏激励他人能力、可能过于批判', 'Lacks drive and ability to inspire others, can be overly critical'),
('Teamworker', '团队工作者', 'Teamworker', '支持团队，温和、敏感且灵活', 'Co-operative, perceptive and diplomatic. Listens and averts friction.', '合作、适应性强、温和、有感知力', 'Co-operative, mild, perceptive, diplomatic', '维护团队和谐、缓解冲突、支持他人', 'Listens, builds, averts friction', '在危机中犹豫不决、难以抉择', 'Indecisive in crunch situations, can be easily influenced'),
('Implementer', '执行者', 'Implementer', '将想法转化为实际行动，纪律性强且高效', 'Practical, reliable, efficient. Turns ideas into actions and organises work that needs to be done.', '纪律性、可靠、高效、保守', 'Disciplined, reliable, conservative, efficient', '组织工作、实施计划、确保质量', 'Turns ideas into practical actions', '缺乏灵活性、可能阻碍变革', 'Somewhat inflexible, slow to respond to new possibilities'),
('Completer_Finisher', '完成者', 'Completer Finisher', '注重细节，确保任务按时高质量完成', 'Painstaking, conscientious, anxious. Searches out errors. Polishes and perfects.', '注重细节、焦虑、追求完美、有责任感', 'Painstaking, conscientious, anxious', '发现错误、确保质量、按时完成任务', 'Searches out errors and omissions, delivers on time', '担心过多、可能悲观、完美主义', 'Inclined to worry unduly, reluctant to delegate'),
('Specialist', '专家', 'Specialist', '提供专业知识和技能，专注于特定领域', 'Single-minded, self-starting, dedicated. Provides knowledge and skills in rare supply.', '专注、自我驱动、追求专业技能', 'Single-minded, self-starting, dedicated', '提供专业知识、维护技术标准', 'Provides knowledge and skills in rare supply', '视野狭窄、难以参与其他领域工作', 'Contributes only on a narrow front, dwells on technicalities');
